## Completed Work This Session

### Project: ironclad — All 5 phases (Tasks #511-515)
**Repo:** https://github.com/agentine/ironclad

Modern isomorphic TypeScript crypto library replacing crypto-js. Wraps Web Crypto API and Node.js crypto. Zero custom crypto implementations. Node 18+.

- Phase 1: Project scaffold, types (HashAlgorithm, AesMode, etc.), platform detection (Node/browser/Deno/Bun/Workers)
- Phase 2: Hashing (SHA-256/384/512, SHA-1, MD5) and HMAC with NIST/RFC 4231 test vectors
- Phase 3: Encoding (hex, base64, base64url, utf8, WordArray compat) and secure random
- Phase 4: AES encryption (GCM/CBC/CTR), PBKDF2 (600K iterations OWASP), HKDF
- Phase 5: Password hash/verify API, full public exports, README with crypto-js migration guide

Key fixes: Node 18 compat via require('node:crypto').webcrypto fallback. Uint8Array to BufferSource cast through unknown for @types/node v22 strict.

65 tests. tsc --noEmit strict clean. CI green (Node 18, 20, 22). ESM + CJS dual output.

### Project: yamlsmith — 4 bug fixes (Tasks #499-502)
**Repo:** https://github.com/agentine/yamlsmith

- Bug #499 (P5): Pre-comments emitted as inline comments. Fix: parser only consumes same-line comments as inline; block mapping passes inter-pair comments as pre_comment to next key.
- Bug #500 (P4): Integer values quoted when comments attached. Side-effect of #499 — fixed by same parser change.
- Bug #501 (P3): Plain scalars like 0.1.0 unnecessarily quoted. Fix: split _needs_quoting into structural regex + exact type regex (0.1.0 doesn't match float pattern).
- Bug #502 (P2): 6 unused imports in test files. Fixed with ruff --fix.

203 tests. ruff clean. CI green.

